#   code snippets + findings, not meant to be tracked.
# skills/auto/ holds agent-auto-captured notes pending user review;
#   once promoted, users can move them to skills/ (which IS tracked
#   when the user chooses).
.prism/second-pass/
.prism/skills/auto/
